
%footer.about
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-3.col-sm-6
        %h3 Comic Artists' Collective
        %p
          Funtime Comics is collective of comics artists and writers based in Christchurch, New Zealand. We aim to provide a forum for the promotion and discussion of the comic medium, promote New Zealand comics and encourage local writers and artists.
      .col-md-3.col-sm-6
        %h3 Get in touch
        %p
          The easiest place to find us is our
          = link_to "Facebook page", "http://www.facebook.com/groups/funtimecomics"
        .adr
          %p.street-address
            10 Ashmole Street
          %p
            %span.locality
              Woolston, Christchurch
            %span.postal-code
              8023
          %p.country-name
            New Zealand
        %p
          = mail_to "funtime@comics.org.nz", "funtime@comics.org.nz", encode: "javascript", class: "email"

      .col-md-3.col-sm-6
        %h3 Workshops
        %p
          Funtime Comics gathers monthly for an afternoon of quality drawing time, tea-drinking and chat. We'd love to meet you, whether you're a longtime comics artist or a complete beginner.
        = link_to "More about Workshops", "/workshops", class: "link-cta"
      .col-md-3.col-sm-6
        %h3 Submissions
        %p
          We take submissions from all over the place, and we put them right here on the website.
        = link_to "More about Subissions", "/submissions", class: "link-cta"
